   Following is the text of the Islamic
Jihad statement threatening to kill foreign hostages as translated
from Arabic to English by The Associated Press:
   In the name of God, the merciful, the compassionate,
   O sons of our Islamic nation,
   O free holy warriors in the world,
   Here is a group of holy warriors undertaking today with all
force and determination a serious attempt to free holy warriors who
sacrificed dearly and who are suffering torture in the prison
dungeons of the oppressive state of Kuwait.
   They have been jailed for confronting the centers of
international arrogance in our Islamic homeland along with regimes
that sold themselves cheaply to the superpowers and their interests
in the region.
   We declare today our full support to the rightful demands of the
hijackers and back them forcefully, and we warn that any
foolhardiness committed against the plane under any pretext or
cover in any form, the Cypriot authorities will bear the full
responsibility for what happens on its territory, which will bring
harm to its government and people.
   To the families of the hostages, we declare that we shall
execute the Western captives in Lebanon if the plane and holy
warriors aboard are subjected to any military foolhardiness.
   The Organization of Islamic Jihad.
   April 1988.
