<HEAD>Dancers From Kirov Ballet Will Perform at Met</HEAD>
<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Two stars from Leningrad's Kirov Ballet will
appear as guest artists with the American Ballet Theater during the
company's spring season at the Metropolitan Opera House.
   Mikhail Baryshnikov, the ABT's artistic director, said Monday
that Altynai Assylmuratova and Faruk Ruzimatov will perform in ``La
